text: Tuberopeplus chilensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1947. It is known from Chile.BioLib.cz - Tuberopeplus chilensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1947
title: Tuberopeplus chilensis
